---
import Layout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Writer, game designer, and collector of stories."
	eyebrow="The Author"
>
	<p>
		This is where your story starts. Write a paragraph or two about who you are, what draws
		you to fantasy worlds and games, and what readers can expect to find here — replace this
		placeholder text in <code>src/pages/about.astro</code>.
	</p>
	<p>
		Talk about your path into creative writing and game design: the first world you built, the
		games that shaped how you think about story, or the moment you realized you wanted to make
		things instead of just consuming them.
	</p>
	<p>
		Close with what you're working on now, and what people can look forward to as this site
		grows.
	</p>
</Layout>
